

Power-OFF Sequence

1. Unmount clients

```bash
sudo umount /mnt/cephfs
sudo umount /mnt/rbd-disk1
```

2. Set Cluster Flags to Pause OSD Operations

```bash
sudo ceph osd set noout
sudo ceph osd set norecover
sudo ceph osd set nobackfill
```

3.  Stop All Ceph Daemons (The Order Matters)

```bash
sudo systemctl stop ceph.target
```

Power-On Sequence (Switch Back On)

1. Power On the Hosts in Order

Boot your virtual machines/servers in this sequence:
* ceph-1 (Let it fully boot first so the leader monitor comes online)
* ceph-2
* ceph-3

2. Clear the Safety Flags

sudo ceph osd unset noout
sudo ceph osd unset norecover
sudo ceph osd unset nobackfill

3. Verify and Remount

```bash
sudo ceph -s
```